text: Andrew Martin (born 4 December 1961) is a former cyclist from Guam. He competed in the team pursuit at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1961 births Category:Living people Category:Guamanian male cyclists Category:Olympic cyclists of Guam Category:Cyclists at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:American track cyclists Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
